__ Cantrip: Bauble __________________________ Cost: 3 ________________________

Use:  cantrip bauble                          Material Component: none
Use:  C bauble

The cantrip bauble is a minor magic of the sphere of summoning.  The cantrip
will create a small purple sphere of solid light.  While the glow from the
bauble is not enough to see by, many bards have been entertained by using 
these objects to < peg > < player name >.
